@benoitsteiner Another friendly request to look at this. To be clear, the bug we are talking about is that the offsets of `extract_glimpse` are not working as expected.

I reproduced the bug using this [slightly larger example](https://gist.github.com/CNugteren/5313ebbd497ddba9016cc2ea09745894) and I got [this output](https://gist.github.com/CNugteren/4d4a236dc1e98784fca8301c098daa51). I cannot make sense of it, and it becomes less clear when trying other input sizes (e.g. 4x4). Also I believe that the bug is also present when the indices are floating point and `normalized=True`.

Note that there is also an issue open on [StackOverflow](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/36039429/tensorflow-extract-glimpse-offset).
